{
  "stem": "13874.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Somehow the refugees were so much better than the American officers who were in charge of us that-- in particular, the one in charge of our particular unit.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't want to mention his name, for I have to say a few very nasty things.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He couldn't handle it-- didn't want to handle it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in that particular case, his German was just what he learned from his parents.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And not-- no-- not much schooling in Germany-- he went to Rochester University.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I have a suspicion that his parents were members of the Bund.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he did not-- but he was a target.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Whatever it is, without going into detail-- it's a story in itself.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Within a week, he was relieved of duty, and I was put in charge of the unit.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Your rank at this time now?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My rank at that time was staff sergeant.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they tried to replace me from intelligence headquarters with another the officer.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they put-- put our colonel, who at that time liked me and what I did; insisted that I will be in charge of his interrogation no matter what they do.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I sent in-- said now-- Evidently I did a good enough job, that six weeks later, I was recommended for a commission.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] [DRINKING] But I was a nasty fellow, and very cocky at that time-- got a few enemies.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So it took about six months until I finally got the commission.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was just the last weeks in the war.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was-- was held up in various places out of spite.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, in France.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The duties-- it was a special kind of interrogation.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
